  <milestone facs="10" n="4r"/>
  <lg>
    <l><seg function="incipit"><lb n="1"/>naṃ tu kathitaṃ tava śobhane |</seg></l>
    <l>etad vādyasamākṣobhaṃ gopanīyaṃ prayatnataḥ |</l>
    <l>ekavīravidhānāni prāg uktaṃ kramapārage |</l>
    <l>atra te kathayeṣyāmi saṃsphaṭaṃ karavalini |:||</l>
  </lg>
  <p><lb n="2"/>iti mālinyonyāsatadhārakramaḥ |:|❈||:|𑇞𑇞𑇞</p>
  <p>śrīdevy uvācaḥ</p>
  <lg>
    <l>śabdarāśis tu ye deva kathaya svaprasādataḥ</l>
    <l>pañcāśabhairavopītam ādhikṣāktuṃ yathā<lb n="3"/>kramaḥ |</l>
  </lg>
  <p><seg function="explicit">śrībhairav uvācaḥ |</seg></p>
